{"tid":1815374,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★口罩缺貨全城瘋搶　藥房以海鮮價出售炒貴4倍","createTime":"2020-01-07T12:47:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T23:24:29.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fd07555df1f4783322ccacfa0db128758a3b3f51","tid":1815374,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e1453a9fd5cc31c9c2b9912.jpg/inpodkygIw97mCg969uDs8WZ7xybXG3VWx5-Z1sefmc?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e1453a9fd5cc31c9c2b9912.jpg%2FinpodkygIw97mCg969uDs8WZ7xybXG3VWx5-Z1sefmc%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=3fb85ba7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢爆發不明原因肺炎，本港亦陸續出現由武漢回港後出現症狀的疑似個案，亦有疑似患者拒絕入院。市民惟恐疫症有機會傳入社區，紛紛購入口罩保護自己。記者今日（7日）到訪荃灣和旺角一帶多間藥房，發現口罩價錢如同「海鮮價」，有藥房將兒童口罩售價炒高近4倍，成人口罩售價亦抬高1倍，仍不乏市民問津。有家長更在社交網站透露，坊間成人口罩已炒至近300元一盒，價錢炒高約6倍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%A6%AA%E5%AD%90/418768/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E7%BC%BA%E8%B2%A8%E5%85%A8%E5%9F%8E%E7%98%8B%E6%90%B6-%E8%97%A5%E6%88%BF%E4%BB%A5%E6%B5%B7%E9%AE%AE%E5%83%B9%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE%E7%82%92%E8%B2%B44%E5%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%2F418768%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E7%25BC%25BA%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%259F%258E%25E7%2598%258B%25E6%2590%25B6-%25E8%2597%25A5%25E6%2588%25BF%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%25AE%25AE%25E5%2583%25B9%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%2594%25AE%25E7%2582%2592%25E8%25B2%25B44%25E5%2580%258D&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TRR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=7ac7c760\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%A6%AA%E5%AD%90/418768/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E7%BC%BA%E8%B2%A8%E5%85%A8%E5%9F%8E%E7%98%8B%E6%90%B6-%E8%97%A5%E6%88%BF%E4%BB%A5%E6%B5%B7%E9%AE%AE%E5%83%B9%E5%87%BA%E5%